Package: uucopTutorials
Title: UUCOP Tutorial Infrastructure
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R:
    person("Andrew", "Castleman", email = "acastleman@uu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Shared infrastructure for UUCOP learnr tutorials. Provides session
    logging, question event tracking, section navigation tracking, student feedback
    forms, deployment helpers, and Google Sheets setup functions. Designed so that
    faculty never need to see or modify infrastructure code.
